data.description: Stunning corner lot with a side yard and alley entrance off the garage. Looking for the historic charm of beautiful built in wood cabinets and original stained glass windows? This home has it all and is ready for it's new owners to make it home! Enjoy the built in storage throughout the home as well as a walk in pantry with storage and never worry about your storage needs. This home features three bedrooms upstairs with a den off the living room on the first floor perfect for that extra space we're all looking for. Looking for a large garage? Here it is! A massive 2.5 car garage with extra parking in your driveway for extra vehicle storage makes this property a dream. Come check it out!
